Palmera at Arabian Ranches is a serene, Mediterranean-inspired villa community nestled within the larger Arabian Ranches development in Dubai. Known for its distinct architecture and tranquil ambiance, Palmera offers a range of two- and three-bedroom villas designed with charming terracotta roofs, arched windows, and lush, landscaped gardens.
The community is divided into four sub-clusters, each featuring its own park and swimming pool, providing residents with a peaceful and family-friendly environment. Palmera’s villas are set amidst winding pathways, palm-lined streets, and tranquil courtyards, creating a picturesque setting that promotes a sense of community and relaxation.
Residents enjoy access to an array of world-class amenities, including the Arabian Ranches Golf Club, equestrian center, tennis courts, and a well-equipped fitness center. The development also includes shopping and dining options at the nearby Arabian Ranches Retail Centre, schools, and healthcare facilities, making it an ideal location for families.
With its strategic location near key road networks, Palmera provides easy access to Dubai’s major attractions and business districts, making it a highly desirable community for those seeking a blend of comfort, luxury, and convenience in a prime residential setting.

Welcome to Villanova, a neighbourhood that you can call your own. Mediterranean inspired cluster homes, townhouses, villas and apartments along with vast open spaces create a serene atmosphere where the community becomes an extended family, and the neighbours become friends.
The Springs is an established gated community that has redefined modern living in Dubai. The Springs comprises clusters of townhouses set as distinct precincts, each with dedicated entry points.

Casa Viva is a new phase of Serena located in Dubailand by Dubai Properties. Just like previous phases in Serena, Casa Viva will be a collection of elegantly designed townhouses surrounded by lush greenery in a peaceful community. 
Development Highlights:

Relax and unwind in spacious Portuguese-styled 2 & 3 bedroom townhouses.
Recreation Community Centre with gym and swimming pool facilities for an active lifestyle.
Located within Dubailand with direct access to Emirates Road for convenient travel.
Enjoy a host of amenities at the Central Plaza in the heart of the community.
Suitable payment plans to move into your dream home.

Live at The Pulse Villas, Dubai South's newest and most coveted neighborhood.This is a master planned community where, in a youthful and vibrant setting, you can experience the Villa & Townhouse lifestyle. Great for families, The Pulse Villas supports a safe and active way of life and encourages it. It is surrounded by greenery with access to a number of state-of-the-art private facilities.
With families in mind, the Pulse Villas have been planned. A private garden, maid's room, closed kitchen, storage room & 2 are included in every house. Shaded parking spots, and with en-suite bathrooms in both bedrooms.

Bianca Townhouses is a new development by Reportage Properties in Dubailand. It is a collection of 653 townhouses with 2, 3, and 4 bedrooms. The townhouses are designed with contemporary architecture and spacious interiors. They feature high-quality finishes and appliances, as well as private balconies or terraces.
Bianca Townhouses is located in the heart of Dubailand, close to all major attractions and amenities. It is just a short drive from the Dubai International Airport, the Mall of the Emirates, and the Burj Khalifa. The development is also surrounded by parks, schools, and mosques.
Why Choose Bianca Townhouses
Bianca Townhouses is a great choice for families, couples, and professionals who are looking for a luxurious and convenient lifestyle in Dubai. The development is perfectly located, offers a variety of amenities, and is built to the highest standards.
The townhouses at Bianca Townhouses offer a variety of amenities, including:

A swimming pool and sundeck
A gym
A children's play area
A barbecue area
A community garden
A 24-hour security system
A parking space for each townhouse

Bianca Townhouses is a great choice for families, couples, and professionals who are looking for a luxurious and convenient lifestyle in Dubai. The development is perfectly located, offers a variety of amenities, and is built to the highest standards.

Maya Townhouses Phase 1 is an elegant residential development located in Wadi Al Safa 3, known for its stylish design and family-friendly environment. This community offers a perfect blend of comfort and sophistication, making it an ideal choice for families seeking a peaceful yet connected lifestyle in Dubai.
Key Features:


Prime Location: Nestled in Wadi Al Safa 3, residents enjoy excellent connectivity to major roadways, providing easy access to key areas of Dubai, including business hubs, shopping destinations, and recreational facilities.


Spacious Townhouses: The development features a range of contemporary townhouses, each designed with open floor plans, high-quality finishes, and ample natural light, ensuring a comfortable and inviting living space for families.


Family-Oriented Amenities: Maya Townhouses Phase 1 offers a variety of amenities, including landscaped gardens, children's play areas, and community parks, promoting an active and social lifestyle for residents of all ages.


Modern Design: The townhouses are characterized by their modern architectural style, incorporating contemporary elements and thoughtful layouts that enhance both functionality and aesthetic appeal.


Secure Living Environment: The community is equipped with 24-hour security, dedicated parking, and maintenance services, ensuring a safe and hassle-free living experience for all residents.


Maya Townhouses Phase 1 presents an exceptional opportunity for families looking to enjoy a luxurious and tranquil lifestyle in Dubai. With its beautiful designs and comprehensive amenities, this development caters to those who value quality living in a serene community setting.
